parts: Aight, lemme spin you some chill beats.  One sec...  (Plays some lofi)  There ya go, don't melt.

Dude, come *on*.  You're better than this slump.  Go grab a coffee, put on some tunes that actually *pump you up* (not that sadboi playlist), and tackle that thing head-on.  You got this.  Or at least, you'll get *something* done, right?  Let's aim for "something" being awesome.
Okay, I *flipped* a coin in my head (because I'm way too cool for actual coins).  It's...heads.  Unless you want me to do it again?  Because I'm feeling pretty lucky today. 😉
